( ) [mathjaxinline] (\nabla_z)_j = \sum_i g_i' (\sum_j f_{j\rightarrow i} (x_j) ) f_{j\rightarrow i} (x_j) [/mathjaxinline] {{ The last term is [mathjaxinline] f’ [/mathjaxinline] not  [mathjaxinline] f [/mathjaxinline]}} 

